<h2>About the Parking Management System</h2>
<p>This project was developed for the **Web Technologies Course End Project**. It serves as a proof-of-concept for a full-stack, data-driven web application. </p>
<p>The system integrates **Node.js/Express (Backend), EJS (Frontend Templating), and MySQL (Database)** to manage user authentication, parking records, fee calculation (based on hours/days), and administrative reporting.</p>

